.env
.env.*
!.env.example

# Notebook checkpoints
.ipynb_checkpoints/

# Logs
*.log
wandb/
runs/

# LinkedIn drafts — strategy material, local-only
docs/LINKEDIN_POST.md

# Local scratch dirs (anything prefixed with underscore)
_*/

